            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> any oceans or coastlines<br/><b>Organization</b> solitary, pair, or team (3\u20135)<br/><b>Treasure</b> NPC gear (masterwork studded leather, sap, masterwork scimitar, shortbow with 20 arrows, <i>potion of eagle\u2019s splendor</i>, <i>potions of invisibility </i>[2], other treasure)"
